pageContext.claim: “This was a thing set up by the Democrats, just like they set up other things -- when you look at what's going on Florida [with the vote count]; when you look at what's going on in lots of different locations.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump regularly blames the Democrats for anything he perceives not to be going his way. However, while the races were tight in Florida, it takes time to count all the votes, including absentee ballots. There's no evidence of voter fraud.
